#2622
Name Base of the Tower~
Desc This room is at the bottom of the watchtower attached to the keep. The main 
hall lies to the east, and cramped barracks are to the south. The walls of 
this room are bare sandstone, with a slate floor. A stone trapdoor with an 
iron ring set in it is close to the west well. Against the north wall is an 
iron ladder, leading up to the watchtower. Since there is no furniture in 
the room, it looks quite bare. 
~
Sector inside~
Owner Barris~
